{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/41392/Urasekai_Picnic", "title": "Urasekai Picnic", "description": "Her first encounter with Toriko Nishina was on the Otherside after seeing \"that thing\" and nearly dying. Ever since that day, exhausted university student Sorawo Kamikoshi's life changed. In this Otherworld, full of mystery, which exists alongside our own, dangerous beings like the Kunekune and Hasshaku-sama that are spoken of in real ghost stories appear. For research, for profit, and to find an important person, Toriko and Sorao set foot into the abnormal.", "genres": "Sci-Fi,Adventure,Mystery,Fantasy,Shoujo Ai"}
{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/40620/Uramichi_Oniisan", "title": "Uramichi Oniisan", "description": "\"Hello, boys and girls! Do you like guys with more than one side to them?\" 31 year old Omota Uramichi is the gymnastics coach in the children's educational TV program \"Together with Mama.\" He might be sweet on the outside, but all boys and girls are inevitably scared off whenever they get a glimpse of the adult darkness that's the result of Uramichi-sensei's emotional instability. This is a tragic eulogy to all the \"boys and girls\" who are now adults!", "genres": "Slice of Life,Comedy"}
{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/43523/Tsuki_ga_Michibiku_Isekai_Douchuu", "title": "Tsuki ga Michibiku Isekai Douchuu", "description": "High school student Misumi Makoto is called into a fantasy world by the god Tsukuyomi, in order to be a hero. However, powerful others in this world aren't as thrilled to have him there, and they kick him to the edge of the world just as Tsukuyomi declares that he must leave Makoto to find his own way. Now it's up to Makoto to find his own way!", "genres": "Adventure,Fantasy"}
