{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/38534/Huoli_Shaonian_Wang_3", "title": "Huoli Shaonian Wang 3", "description": "Huoli Shaonian Wang is a Chinese multi-media franchise created to sell yoyo toys to children. Huoli Shaonian Wang 3 is the first animated season in the franchise but the 3rd story chronologically. The show focuses on competitive schools that hold yo-yo contests. Each team has their own issues that they solve. Each yoyo has a name that reflects the toy's design. The show makes use of minor special effects in order to portray magic/spirit/chi and the speed of the yoyo. These \"magic spells\" are \"battling\" and the person whose \"magic\" remains, wins.", "genres": "Game,Kids"}
