{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/38128/Zhu_Zhu_Xia__Guang_Ming_Shou_Wei_Zhe", "title": "Zhu Zhu Xia: Guang Ming Shou Wei Zhe", "description": "Twin City, as legend has it, is an evil city which was born at the time when Crystal City was created. There is a mirror-like lake above the city which has a horrifying power. It enables people to face the darkest side deep within their hearts. This darkness manifests as the person's opposite. The heroes must send these malicious beings back to their realm before they tear Crystal City apart.", "genres": "Kids,Sci-Fi,Super Power"}
{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/38122/Zhu_Zhu_Xia__Jimu_Shijie_de_Tonghua", "title": "Zhu Zhu Xia: Jimu Shijie de Tonghua", "description": "When GG Bond's grandfather, EE Bond, tries to save the dinosaur from extinction by traveling back 60 million years, he accidentally winds up in the Brick Kingdom, a fairy tale world built by blocks, along with half of the rest of the city. Since they cannot leave, they slowly transform the world with technology like their own. His grandson, GG Bond, follows in his grandfather's footsteps as an Assembler, somebody who can build the blocks of the Brick Kingdom into anything. He uses these skills to fight evil.", "genres": "Sci-Fi,Super Power,Kids,Fantasy"}
