{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/10958/High_Score", "title": "High Score", "description": "A school comedy with violent and blue jokes. Fujiwara Megumi is a beautiful high school girl but has a selfish and violent character. She has a boyfriend named Matsumoto Masamune, but she often goes around with other boys, who end up as victims due to her selfish behavior.", "genres": "Slice of Life,Comedy,School,Shoujo"}
