{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/17969/Tanken_Driland__1000-nen_no_Mahou", "title": "Tanken Driland: 1000-nen no Mahou", "description": "1,000 years after Princess Mikoto's era, all hunters have been sealed into cards due to a certain incident in the past. Adventurous boy Hagan becomes the key to freeing these sealed hunters, and travels along with his friends to find these cards, sometimes facing treacherous battles.", "genres": "Adventure,Fantasy"}
