{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/8964/Stitch__Zutto_Saikou_no_Tomodachi", "title": "Stitch!: Zutto Saikou no Tomodachi", "description": "In their new adventure, Yuuna and Stitch move from their small island Izayoi to the Okinawa main island where Yuuna is supposed to visit a school. A new cast of friends awaits them there as well as a new crisis approaching from space.", "genres": "Adventure,Comedy,Kids"}
