{"url": "https://myanimelist.net/anime/2234/Panda-Z__The_Robonimation", "title": "Panda-Z: The Robonimation", "description": "Panda-Z chronicles the misadventures of Pan Taron and his giant robot Panda-Z, as they battle the evil Skull Panda and his Warunimal forces.", "genres": "Action,Comedy,Kids,Mecha,Parody,Sci-Fi,Shounen"}
